These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: animationsy, time-travel, animation, thriller, spy, mystery, epic
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, november, april, may, july, march, august
The people have 7 different jobs:  software-developer, photographer, project-manager, mechanic, nurse, teacher, police-officer
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, aristoff, tiparillo, prince, swisher, dunhill, havana
 1. the mechanic is on the far right##1
 2. the nurse is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the swisher-smoker is the project-manager##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is the project-manager##1
 7. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the prince-smoker is between the havana-smoker and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1
11. the software-developer is the person watching spy movies##1
12. the person watching spy movies is the bongani-smoker##1
13. the person watching animationsy movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
14. the person who's birthday is in march is the tiparillo-smoker##1
15. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
16. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
17. the teacher is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
18. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
19. the police-officer is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Movie-Genre      | time-travel  | mystery        | spy | animation      | thriller     | animationsy      | epic     |
| Birthday   | november | may         | august   | october | march    | july | april |
| Job         | project-manager | nurse | software-developer | photographer | police-officer  | teacher  | mechanic    |
| Cigar     | swisher  | dunhill         | bongani     | aristoff    | tiparillo | prince     | havana     |

