7 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, canasta, whist, bridge, monopoly, go
7 different pets are kept: bird, horse, guinea-pig, turtle, chinchilla, ferret, snake
 1. the nigerian is the old-henry-smoker##1
 2. the german is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the malaysian##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
