 8. the person playing go is the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the egyptian##1
10. the person playing whist is between the person playing canasta and the ritmeester-smoker##2
11. the person playing scrabble is the old-henry-smoker##1
12. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
13. the person playing bridge is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person playing monopoly##2
14. the american is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
15. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
16. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
17. the havana-smoker is on the left of the canadian##1
18. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
19. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
